{
  "stem": "14737.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, this street they called it Synagogue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I go there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And many-- a few other [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we see big synagogue is burning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened is the following, that the night, they burn-- they start to burn the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How would this synagogue found itself on a place where among them were houses, big houses, factories?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And German guards were standing there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the firemen came to make out the fire, but didn't allow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They already were protecting there that the certain other houses shouldn't catch on also fire.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was witnessing, myself, this big, great synagogue in Brno.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least 3,000 people were sitting there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went many times where one of the most famous cantors was by the name of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was burned down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how it burned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Burned down to ashes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I was there about a few years ago.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now there is nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's only some sort of a garage place or a-- what, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have some picture of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was witnessing, myself, the big synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And large demonstration started against Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Brno, the population at that time at least of 300,000.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jews didn't' left too many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jews about, I would say, 8,000, 10,000, but demonstrations every day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you could see SS people and a lot of collaborators.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jews ?] lived-- in Brno lived a lot of Germans also, collaborators.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could see in the [? white socks ?] going, singing in the streets, and big, big demonstrations, all kinds of slogans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And came a Friday.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Next day, we were on the 7th-- this was on the 17th of, of March, when the synagogue was burned.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
